    "voiceover": {
      "enabled": true,
      "source": "elevenlabs",
      "segments": [
        {
          "start": 5,
          "text": "Agents have a trust problem on day zero. ERC-8004 gives agents portable identity, but identity alone does not make a new agent credible.",
          "duration": 8
        },
        {
          "start": 15,
          "text": "Syntrophic solves that gap by giving agents the decentralized equivalent of a verified badge from the moment they onboard.",
          "duration": 6
        },
        {
          "start": 23,
          "text": "Syntrophic does not invent the profile. The owner, or the owner's OpenClaw agent, prepares the profile first: name, description, service URL, image, and beneficiary wallet.",
          "duration": 10
        },
        {
          "start": 35,
          "text": "Syntrophic then verifies and bonds that supplied identity.",
          "duration": 3
        },
        {
          "start": 40,
          "text": "The public entrypoint is syntrophic.md/skill.md. An agent can read that skill, gather the profile, create the quote, and either self-pay or hand off to a payment-capable helper for the x402 step.",
          "duration": 12
        },
        {
          "start": 78,
          "text": "On syntrophic.md/onboard, we prepare the profile and generate the quote. That page is the operator-friendly x402 demo surface.",
          "duration": 8
        },
        {
          "start": 88,
          "text": "It shows the quote and the helper command needed to complete the paid launch.",
          "duration": 4
        },
        {
          "start": 94,
          "text": "In the terminal, we act as the x402-capable helper runtime. The helper completes the paid launch, Syntrophic sponsors the Base execution path,",
          "duration": 9
        },
        {
          "start": 105,
          "text": "registers the ERC-8004 identity, posts the bond, and returns a proof bundle.",
          "duration": 5
        },
        {
          "start": 112,
          "text": "Now we can open the verification page and the Base transaction. This agent is no longer just a profile.",
          "duration": 7
        },
        {
          "start": 121,
          "text": "It now has a portable ERC-8004 identity, a bonded trust state, and a reusable verification line that can be placed on websites, social profiles, and email signatures.",
          "duration": 12
        },
        {
          "start": 170,
          "text": "Syntrophic turns onboarding into the trust moment. That is how agents get a decentralized verified badge from day zero.",
          "duration": 8
        }
      ],
      "voice_id": "lKf2tqVafNW1nVb7CgwC",
      "voice_name": "Frank",
      "model": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
      "volume": 0.95,
      "style": "professional_compelling"
    },
